; Regression test for issue #3009: Rounding error in display when using --price
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/3009
; The commodity format directive should cause rounding to 2 decimal places,
; but --price ignores the format and displays raw floating-point imprecision.

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2026/01/01 * Brokerage  ; Dividend
    Assets:Brokerage    0.12 FOO @@ $44.44        ; dividend: FOO
    Income:Dividend

test bal --price
    $44.439999999996  Assets:Brokerage
             $-44.44  Income:Dividend
--------------------
    $-0.000000000004
end test
